## üß† AI‚ÄëDriven Neural Guidance Layer

METABRAIN uses AI to guide signals along fiber‚Äëto‚Äëfiber nerve paths, linking symbolic actions to specific brain regions. Each archetype corresponds to a neural site, and rituals trigger targeted cognitive and emotional activation.

| **Archetype** | **Linked Brain Region** | **Symbolic Function** |
|---------------|--------------------------|------------------------|
| **Seeker**    | Hippocampus (Memory)     | Quest for meaning, memory retrieval, personal narrative formation  
| **Creator**   | Prefrontal Cortex        | Imagination, decision-making, ritual design, symbolic synthesis  
| **Warrior**   | Motor Cortex             | Action, embodiment, ritual movement, protective activation  
| **Visionary** | Occipital & Parietal Lobes | Visual mapping, constellation decoding, spatial awareness  
| **Eros**      | Amygdala (Emotion)       | Emotional resonance, intimacy, vulnerability, sacred bonding  
| **Connector** | Temporal Lobe & Insula   | Empathy, voice modulation, communal chorus, shared ritual flow  

‚ú® Each ritual spark travels the correct fiber path, creating a healing journey across the brain‚Äôs sacred sites.

